{"tid":1991281,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"耿爽: 國際獨立調查病毒源頭與攜手抗疫氛圍並不相符","createTime":"2020-04-27T10:22:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T14:00:11.000Z","uid":240362,"like":24,"dislike":144,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"9ef2d9c30dc02396fada66b87a0eb7451b3ac395","tid":1991281,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T10:22:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523007-20200427.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523007-20200427.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4Ux5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=f2b9b580\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523007-20200427.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e9d0c1ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523007-20200427.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n部分國家要求對中國早期應對疫情方面，展開國際獨立調查。在北京，外交部發言人耿爽強調，中國是首先報告新冠肺炎疫情的國家，但並不意味中國就是病毒的源頭，中方亦多次講過，病毒源頭問題是科學問題，需要交給科學家及專業人士研究。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽批評，部分人鼓吹或鼓譟所謂調查，與當前國際社會攜手抗擊疫情的氛圍並不相符，他們藉此進行政治操弄，亦是不得人心，強調目前最重要是防止疫情再次發生，而不是去指責或歸咎他人，更加不是搞甚麼追責及索賠，因為國際上無這種先例，亦無法律依據。"},{"pid":"c3b8f776b7236300663b72835e08e51983d6ff61","tid":1991281,"uid":321977,"like":165,"dislike":1,"score":164,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T10:23:24.000Z","msg":"邊個同你攜手，掂到你都要消毒啦on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd6e05d207c6b880e0b81e1255a654ba117336e","tid":1991281,"uid":80724,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T10:24:06.000Z","msg":"驚啦開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d73db1872a83fd2f48f20810fdcdbb6a576dbf","tid":1991281,"uid":107577,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T10:24:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Twitter 國際戰線需要你<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\